t loops I have sold them to vendors for just under 300 pp each. Also just like the other two places that I have mentioned already the giants also drop pages for your spell research. I hope that this will help your chanter out and if you have any questions don't hesitate to give me a shout. May you walk in peace and may the sun smile warmly upon you. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub76.ezboard.com/frandomactsfrm10.showPrevMessage?topicID=161.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub76.ezboard.com/frandomactsfrm10.showNextMessage?topicID=161.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub76.ezboard.com/frandomactsfrm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=161.topic&index=3><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub76.ezboard.com/frandomactsfrm10.emailToFriend?topicID=161.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub76.ezboard.com/frandomactsfrm10.threadControl?topicID=161.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub76.ezboard.com/frandomactsfrm10.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=161.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub76.ezboard.com/frandomactsfrm10.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=161.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub76.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump t